{ Black will take on c3 at the right moment, waiting for a3 or when white can retreat/defend the c3-knight. White's pawn structure will be worse after doubling pawns on c3 and/or g3. }
9. e3 f5 { No rush to take on c3 or g3. We keep strengthening the center. } 10.
Bd3 Bxc3+ 11. bxc3 d6
