{ Black has more pieces developed, so it is easier to play for black. } 9. e3
{ 9.Nb5  is the move to look at. Otherwise,  we stop Nb5 and keep improving our position. }
9... a6
{ The position is balanced. Not too much to add, it is a normal position. } *

