11... Bxf6 12. Qe4 O-O 13. Qxa8 { The rook is untouchable. } 13... Nc6 14. Qb7
Rb8 { The white queen is trapped. } 15. Qxb8+ Nxb8 16. a4 c6 17. Be2 a6
{ Black has got the queen and a pawn for the two rooks, so you could say that the material is balanced.  However, the rooks do not have good open files yet. Meanwhile, the queen can infiltrate through d6-b4 or c7-a5, causing problems for white alongside the queenside pawns majority. }
