9... Kh8
{ Sidestepping the check!  (with dxe6 and exf7+)  We can get a position with equal material and a better pawn structure @@StartBracket@@like in some previous lines alike the Nimzo-Indian@@EndBracket@@. }
10. dxe6 { Now we get a better position. } 10... Bxg2 11. Nxg2 fxe6
{ With equal material and a better structure. A knight on c5/a5 will be very strong. }
