10. Bg5 { Very rarely played. } 10... h6 11. Bxf6
{ More logical with white's previous move. } 11... Nxf6 12. Ne5 c5
{ With an equal position. It will probably lead to positions with hanging pawns. We play like in those positions since this one has nothing special. }
