13. Bf4 g5 { Another only move. } 14. Rad1 Qc5 15. b4 Qxb4 16. Bd2 Qc5 17. Bxe4
Bxe4 18. Qxe4
{ After several only moves in order not to get a losing position, black only reaches a worse position. Black will have to fight hard to survive the wrecked kingside. }
