17. Nxd5 { Again, the savior knight. } 17... Bxf2+
{ The other idea behind our previous move.  We are threatening to win the exchange with 18...Qc5+ and 19...Rxc1.   17...exd5  is also possible  18.Rxc4  Qxc4  19.Qxd7  Qxe2  with an equal position with equal material. }
18. Kh1 exd5 { We are headed to some exchanges. } 19. Rxc4 Qxc4 20. Qxd7 Qxe2
{ With an equal position despite our temporary extra pawn. } *

