{ I do not like this move, the e1-rook is doing nothing and weakens the f2-pawn @@StartBracket@@ Ndf6-Ng4 is possible@@EndBracket@@. White remains in the game, but black's position seems way more comfortable. White wants to double rooks on the c-file, but there are better ways to do it like Rc2 first. }
