16... Bf6 17. Ng5 g6 18. Rg4 Bxc3 19. Qxc3 Na4 20. Qd4 Re8
{ After a few tempo moves @@StartBracket@@taking pieces, attacking the queen, ...@@EndBracket@@ black's pieces are joining the attack on the queenside. The rest of the game is not that important, black just tops off his foe. }
